### Complete Social Share Task with Location Tracking
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/share-social
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
accept-version: {{apiVersion}}
x-user-id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proofUrl": "https://twitter.com/user/status/1234567890",
  "latitude": 35.6762,
  "longitude": 139.6503
}

### Complete Social Share Task without Location (backward compatible)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}/share-social
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
accept-version: {{apiVersion}}
x-user-id: {{userId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "proofUrl": "https://instagram.com/p/ABCD1234/"
}

